		<tbody>
			<tr>
			<th colspan=6><bidding>-,1C,1D,?</bidding></th>
			</tr>
			<tr>
			<th>Отв</th><th>Action</th><th>HCP</th><th>Прим</th><th colspan=2>Откр </th>
			</tr>
			<tr><td>X</td><td>F1</td><td class="hcp_light">&nbsp;6+&nbsp;</td><td><span class="span2">&nbsp;4+<span class="red_card">♥</span>&nbsp;</span>&nbsp;<span class="span2">&nbsp;4+♠&nbsp;</span></td><td colspan=2></td></tr>
			<tr><td>1<span class="red_card">♥</span></td><td>—</td><td class="hcp_light">&nbsp;6+&nbsp;</td><td><span class="span2">&nbsp;4+<span class="red_card">♥</span>&nbsp;</span></td><td colspan=2></td></tr>
			<tr><td>1♠</td><td>—</td><td class="hcp_light">&nbsp;6+&nbsp;</td><td>&nbsp;<span class="span2">&nbsp;4+♠&nbsp;</span></td><td colspan=2></td></tr>
		</tbody>
	</table>
	</center>
	
	<h3>Пример 5</h3>
	<center>
	<bidding>-,1C,1D, X,P,1H,P,?</bidding>
	<br>
	<hand>S|AT52.AQ62.654.96</hand>
	<p>У нас <span class="hcp_light">&nbsp;18&nbsp;</span>. Учитывая согласованный фит <span class="red_card">♥</span> и синглет в ♠. Наш ответ: <strong>4<span class="red_card">♥</span></strong>.</p>
	</center>
